channel.title: [Project Insanity] "HighTivity" 317 Spawin PKIng Server! Need a partner!
channel.description:
[center][img]http://hightivity.com/banner.png[/img][/center]
Hello. I am making a project named HighTivity, and rather not do it by myself.
What will [b]I[/b] be doing in this partnership? Paying for the VPS Paying for the Web Hosting + Domain (.com) Making sure people are following rules etc. Handeling donations
What will [b]you[/b] be doing? Coding Moderating forums + a little in game.
Features: Ancient Magics Spawning Smudged items Lunars Dragon Claws Chaotic Vestas
Basically your original PI server with some extras.
Pictures: [img]http://hightivity.com/uploads/1309319614.png[/img]
Videos:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UDjndcPRt-0
You will recieve 50% of the donations we [b]profit[/b] (that means after the vps, webhosting + domain is paid off)
I'm planning to have atleast 20 people on at a time.
Yes I already bought the web hosting and the domain, but I don't know if I'm allowed to advertise. But if you look HighTivity up on google, it'll be like the 4th link.
I don't have much to say, but if you're interested reply, if not don't bother replying.
Need a picture of gameplay? PM me.
Anyways I'll buy the VPS once people start making accounts on the forums. (Real people)
Thanks, anthonyduka
